<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="en"> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <title>GenAI ContentOps 2.0 — Architecture</title> <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Syne:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <style> *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; } :root { --bg: #060810; --card: #0d1117; --border: #1e2736; --draft: #00e5a0; --comply: #ff6b35; --local: #4da6ff; --distrib: #c77dff; --intel: #ffda6b; --text: #e8edf5; --muted: #6b7a99; --glow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,229,160,0.15); } body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; } /* Grid bg */ body::before { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; } .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; } /* HERO */ .hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 80px; } .badge { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00e5a0, #4da6ff); color: #060810; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; } h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.05; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #6b7a99 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; margin-bottom: 16px; } .subtitle { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; } /* PIPELINE FLOW */ .pipeline { display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 80px; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 8px; } .agent-block { flex: 1; min-width: 160px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 28px 18px; text-align: center; position: relative; cursor: default; transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s; animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; } .agent-block:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); } .agent-block:not(:last-child)::after { content: '→'; position: absolute; right: -22px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--muted); z-index: 10; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; } .agent-block + .agent-block { margin-left: 28px; } .agent-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; display: block; } .agent-name { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; } .agent-desc { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; } .agent-tag { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.65rem; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px; margin-top: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.05em; } /* Per-agent colors */ .a-draft { border-top: 3px solid var(--draft); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,229,160,0.08); } .a-draft:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,229,160,0.18); } .a-draft .agent-tag { background: rgba(0,229,160,0.12); color: var(--draft); } .a-comply { border-top: 3px solid var(--comply); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,107,53,0.08); } .a-comply:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(255,107,53,0.2); } .a-comply .agent-tag { background: rgba(255,107,53,0.12); color: var(--comply); } .a-local { border-top: 3px solid var(--local); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(77,166,255,0.08); } .a-local:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(77,166,255,0.2); } .a-local .agent-tag { background: rgba(77,166,255,0.12); color: var(--local); } .a-dist { border-top: 3px solid var(--distrib);box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(199,125,255,0.08); } .a-dist:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(199,125,255,0.2); } .a-dist .agent-tag { background: rgba(199,125,255,0.12); color: var(--distrib); } .a-intel { border-top: 3px solid var(--intel); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,218,107,0.08); } .a-intel:hover { box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(255,218,107,0.2); } .a-intel .agent-tag { background: rgba(255,218,107,0.12); color: var(--intel); } /* FEEDBACK LOOP */ .feedback-bar { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,229,160,0.06), rgba(77,166,255,0.06)); border: 1px dashed rgba(0,229,160,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 24px; margin-bottom: 80px; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.4s ease both; } .feedback-bar strong { color: var(--draft); } .loop-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; } /* DETAILS GRID */ .section-title { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 32px; color: var(--text); } .section-title span { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--muted); vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 12px; } .detail-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 60px; } .detail-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; } .detail-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; } .detail-card ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; } .detail-card li { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); padding: 8px 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; border-left: 2px solid var(--border); } .detail-card li::before { content: attr(data-icon); font-size: 1rem; } /* DEMO STEPS */ .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 60px; } .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 24px; animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; } .step-num { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00e5a0, #4da6ff); color: #060810; font-weight: 800; font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; } .step-content h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 6px; } .step-content p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; } .step-content code { font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; color: var(--draft); } /* TECH STACK */ .tech-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 60px; } .tech-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 20px; text-align: center; animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; transition: border-color 0.2s; } .tech-card:hover { border-color: rgba(0,229,160,0.3); } .tech-card .t-icon { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 8px; } .tech-card .t-name { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; } .tech-card .t-role { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--muted); } /* FOOTER */ footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px 0 20px; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); } @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } } @media (max-width: 700px) { .pipeline { flex-direction: column; } .agent-block:not(:last-child)::after { content: '↓'; right: 50%; transform: translateX(50%); bottom: -22px; top: auto; } .agent-block + .agent-block { margin-left: 0; margin-top: 28px; } .detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .tech-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } } </style> </head> <body> <div class="wrap"> <!-- HERO --> <div class="hero"> <div class="badge">🏆 Hackathon Ready · Multi-Agent AI Platform</div> <h1>GenAI ContentOps 2.0</h1> <p class="subtitle">Autonomous 5-agent pipeline for compliant, localized, and self-optimizing enterprise content — built for the Indian market.</p> </div> <!-- PIPELINE --> <div class="pipeline"> <div class="agent-block a-draft" style="animation-delay:0.0s"> <span class="agent-icon">📝</span> <div class="agent-name">Draft Agent</div> <div class="agent-desc">Generates blog or social content using Claude AI</div> <span class="agent-tag">AGENT 1</span> </div> <div class="agent-block a-comply" style="animation-delay:0.08s"> <span class="agent-icon">🔍</span> <div class="agent-name">Compliance Agent</div> <div class="agent-desc">Detects risky claims & regulatory violations</div> <span class="agent-tag">AGENT 2</span> </div> <div class="agent-block a-local" style="animation-delay:0.16s"> <span class="agent-icon">🌐</span> <div class="agent-name">Localization Agent</div> <div class="agent-desc">Translates to Hindi + Hinglish for Indian audience</div> <span class="agent-tag">AGENT 3</span> </div> <div class="agent-block a-dist" style="animation-delay:0.24s"> <span class="agent-icon">📡</span> <div class="agent-name">Distribution Agent</div> <div class="agent-desc">Posts to LinkedIn, Twitter, Facebook & more</div> <span class="agent-tag">AGENT 4</span> </div> <div class="agent-block a-intel" style="animation-delay:0.32s"> <span class="agent-icon">🧠</span> <div class="agent-name">Intelligence Agent</div> <div class="agent-desc">Analytics, sentiment & improvement suggestions</div> <span class="agent-tag">AGENT 5</span> </div> </div> <!-- FEEDBACK LOOP --> <div class="feedback-bar"> <span class="loop-icon">🔄</span> <div> <strong>Feedback Loop:</strong> Intelligence Agent generates improvement suggestions → suggestions are passed back to the Draft Agent on the next run → content quality improves autonomously over time. </div> </div> <!-- DETAILS --> <h2 class="section-title">Agent Details <span>what each one does</span></h2> <div class="detail-grid"> <div class="detail-card"> <h3>📝 Draft Agent</h3> <ul> <li data-icon="→">Input: topic + content_type (blog/social)</li> <li data-icon="→">Claude claude-sonnet-4-20250514 generates structured content</li> <li data-icon="→">Adapts based on previous feedback</li> <li data-icon="→">Output: title, body, word count</li> </ul> </div> <div class="detail-card"> <h3>🔍 Compliance Agent</h3> <ul> <li data-icon="→">Rule-based keyword scanner (25+ risky phrases)</li> <li data-icon="→">AI review for SEBI, RBI, ASCI guidelines</li> <li data-icon="→">Status: PASS / WARNING / FAIL</li> <li data-icon="→">Auto-corrects non-compliant content</li> </ul> </div> <div class="detail-card"> <h3>🌐 Localization Agent</h3> <ul> <li data-icon="→">Full Hindi translation (Devanagari script)</li> <li data-icon="→">Hinglish: natural Roman-script Hindi-English mix</li> <li data-icon="→">Tone adapted for urban Indian professionals</li> <li data-icon="→">Preserves content structure across languages</li> </ul> </div> <div class="detail-card"> <h3>📡 Distribution Agent</h3> <ul> <li data-icon="→">Simulates 6 channels: LinkedIn, Twitter, Instagram...</li> <li data-icon="→">Routes correct language per channel</li> <li data-icon="→">Logs estimated reach per channel</li> <li data-icon="→">Easy to replace with real API calls</li> </ul> </div> </div> <!-- DEMO STEPS --> <h2 class="section-title">Demo Steps <span>for judges</span></h2> <div class="steps"> <div class="step" style="animation-delay:0.0s"> <div class="step-num">1</div> <div class="step-content"> <h4>Launch the Platform</h4> <p>Start FastAPI: <code>python main.py</code> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Start Dashboard: <code>streamlit run dashboard.py</code><br>Show the green "API Connected" indicator in the sidebar.</p> </div> </div> <div class="step" style="animation-delay:0.05s"> <div class="step-num">2</div> <div class="step-content"> <h4>Enter a Compelling Topic</h4> <p>Try: <em>"How Generative AI is transforming MSME lending in India"</em><br>Select Blog Post, click <strong>Run Full Pipeline</strong>.</p> </div> </div> <div class="step" style="animation-delay:0.1s"> <div class="step-num">3</div> <div class="step-content"> <h4>Walk Through Each Tab</h4> <p>Draft → Compliance check → Hindi/Hinglish translations → Distribution log → Analytics & grade. Highlight the <strong>3-language output</strong> — judges love this.</p> </div> </div> <div class="step" style="animation-delay:0.15s"> <div class="step-num">4</div> <div class="step-content"> <h4>Demonstrate the Feedback Loop</h4> <p>Copy improvement suggestions → Enable Feedback Loop → Run again with same topic. Show how the new draft incorporates the suggestions. <strong>This closes the autonomous loop.</strong></p> </div> </div> <div class="step" style="animation-delay:0.2s"> <div class="step-num">5</div> <div class="step-content"> <h4>Show the API Docs</h4> <p>Open <code>http://localhost:8000/docs</code> to show the production-ready FastAPI Swagger UI. Hit <code>/runs</code> to show the SQLite history.</p> </div> </div> </div> <!-- TECH STACK --> <h2 class="section-title">Tech Stack <span>what's under the hood</span></h2> <div class="tech-grid"> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">🐍</div><div class="t-name">Python 3.10+</div><div class="t-role">Core language</div></div> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">⚡</div><div class="t-name">FastAPI</div><div class="t-role">REST API + orchestration</div></div> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">🤖</div><div class="t-name">Claude claude-sonnet-4-20250514</div><div class="t-role">Content generation & AI</div></div> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">🗄️</div><div class="t-name">SQLite</div><div class="t-role">Run history & feedback</div></div> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">📊</div><div class="t-name">Streamlit</div><div class="t-role">Interactive dashboard</div></div> <div class="tech-card"><div class="t-icon">🔗</div><div class="t-name">Anthropic SDK</div><div class="t-role">Claude API client</div></div> </div> <footer> GenAI ContentOps 2.0 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 5-Agent Autonomous Pipeline &nbsp;·&nbsp; Built for Hackathon &nbsp;·&nbsp; Indian Enterprise Focus </footer> </div> </body> </html>